title: Firearms Expert Reacts To Counter-Strike 2’s Guns PART 2
description: Jonathan Ferguson, a weapons expert and Keeper of Firearms & Artillery at the Royal Armouries, breaks down more of the weaponry of Counter-Strike 2, including the R8 Revolver, M4A4, and MAG-7. We even traumatize Jonathan a little with a peculiar PP-Bizon!

title: Every Peter Parker Suit in Marvel's Spider-Man 2 (Spoilers)
description: Peter's wardrobe has only grown with 34 suits to unlock, plus 5 bonus suits from the deluxe edition.
